overview.en: CoinBull aims to build a one-stop user experience and ecological system of‘Market+Data+Community+Information+Trading+Finance’. NNB is the token of CoinBull platform , and NNB will circulate in the ecology of CoinBull.
overview.zh: 币牛牛致力于打造“行情+数据+社区+资讯+交易+金融”的一站式用户体验和生态体系，NNB是币牛牛平台的代币，NNB将在币牛牛生态中流通。
